reviewText:
This VHS tape is very well done and easy to follow along and understand, about 50 minutes long.
An excellent source for anyone baking with yeast doughs.
Demonstrates how to shape and make Parker House Rolls,
Clover Leafs, Kaisers.  Cinnamon Rolls, Jelly Rolls,
Monkey Bread.  English Muffins, Bagels and Pretzels.
  Helpful for a seasoned baker or a beginner baker.
They make it easy to follow.  You will enjoy watching
this video and be successful in your own baking.
